Package: rtemis.core
Title: Type Checking and Validation
Version: 0.0.3
Date: 2026-04-19
Authors@R: person(given = "E.D.", family = "Gennatas", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), 
    email = "gennatas@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9280-3609"))
Description: Utilities for type checking, argument validation, and input
    cleaning. Includes the rtemis msg messaging system and the fmt formatting system. Provides 
    test_* functions that return logical values, check_* functions that throw informative errors, 
    and clean_* functions that return validated and coerced inputs.
